Original workout description: This 10 minute guided meditation for positivity is the perfect way to welcome peace, focus, and a positive mind. Let go of anxiety, fear and worries and reset with healing energy for productivity and a perfect day. Through the simple act of reconnecting with your inner self, this easy Boho Beautiful guided meditation is perfect for anyone that is needing some positivity and calm during stressful and uncertain times. 

It is time to let go of the negativity, stress, anxiety....whatever is holding you back in your life. Let this guided meditation with Juliana Spicoluk take you on a meditative journey to cleanse and heal yourself from the inside out. 

So find a quiet space, put some headphones on, close your eyes, and enjoy.
